About: ka_science, i decided to try something new.. and this is the map. A Science warehouse thing. With a Floating LaZoR containment unit in the center. A laser shoots out the lower bit, requiring you jump over it to battle your opponent.

(YAY) Short Story: Tom_Tom's scientists have discovered the power of LaZoRs. They constructed the laser in their science warehouse thing. Soon after the laser went crazy and began cutting his scientists in half :*(. 

Enjoy, max players 14. Size small.
